  <brief_title>Modified Triple Osteotomy for Acetabular Dysplasia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Modified Triple Osteotomy for Acetabular Dysplasia - A Modified Technique for Better Femoral Head Medialization and Coverage</official_title>
